147866.name: Number of maternal deaths
147866.description: A maternal death refers to the death of a woman while pregnant or within 42 days of termination of pregnancy, irrespective of the duration and site of the pregnancy, from any cause related to or aggravated by the pregnancy or its management but not from accidental or incidental causes.

source.name: World Health Organization (via World Bank)
source.dataPublisherSource: Trends in Maternal Mortality - World Health Organization (2019)
